creator: FFZ srl
descriptionHtml:
Professional barometer. You can view in real time the progress of the atmospheric pressure and then providing the change in the weather time. absolute precision through the parallel operation of different sensors, such as pressure sensor the device, GPS sensor, and remote connection time to nearby weather stations to you.
Proposes a barometer with analog dial, available both with international measurements (hPa) with both Anglo measure (inHg), you can see in addition to the weather forecast, also the temperature and the percentage of moisture in the air. E 'can also see the pressure change in the last 24 hours through a histogram graph, and see through a graphical map of your GPS position.
Also interesting is the ability to take a photograph with the superimposed weather data and some effects that can be activated under certain weather conditions and share them with the most popular social networks: facebook, whatsapp, instagram, email etc..
If you want you can also install the widget to keep an eye on the weather and atmospheric pressure.
descriptionShort: Turn your device into a professional barometer. Share photos

title: Professional barometer

container.value:
Via del Melo, 32 - Fraz. Semonte
06024 Gubbio (PG) ITALY

creator: FFZ srl
descriptionHtml:
Professional barometer. You can view in real time the progress of the atmospheric pressure and then providing the change in the weather time. absolute precision through the parallel operation of different sensors, such as pressure sensor the device, GPS sensor, and remote connection time to nearby weather stations to you.
Proposes a barometer with analog dial, available both with international measurements (hPa) with both Anglo measure (inHg), you can see in addition to the weather forecast, also the temperature and the percentage of moisture in the air. E 'can also see the pressure change in the last 24 hours through a histogram graph, and see through a graphical map of your GPS position.
Also interesting is the ability to take a photograph with the superimposed weather data and some effects that can be activated under certain weather conditions and share them with the most popular social networks: facebook, whatsapp, instagram, email etc..
If you want you can also install the widget to keep an eye on the weather and atmospheric pressure.
descriptionShort: Turn your device into a professional barometer. Share photos
